title: Paco De Lucia - 1987 - Siroco [EAC-APE]
description:
I've looked for this album for a long time in the internet but without success, the 

only format available out there was mp3 so i decided to buy this precious album and 

to share it with all paco de lucia fans, this is paco at his best, this is his crown 

achievement and for me personally the best guitar album of all time, presented to 

you in lossless quality :D enjoy!
